# Project-Wide Rules

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 14 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + Custom CSS
- **Email**: Resend API
- **Deployment**: IONOS (GitHub Actions + SFTP) + Cloudflare

## Required: Use Project Skills

Before implementing tasks, read relevant skills from `plugins/portfolio-tools/skills/`:

| Task Type | Required Skill(s) |
|-----------|-------------------|
| UI/CSS changes | `design-system/SKILL.md`, `visual-hierarchy/SKILL.md` |
| Case study work | `case-study-builder/SKILL.md` |
